Indulge in Peranakan sweets with the &ldquo;Pay 1 Dine 2 Afternoon High Tea&rdquo; at Hari&rsquo;s Bar Lobby &amp; Lounge.
Source: Holiday Inn Singapore Orchard City Centre. Pink kuih lapis is on the menu at the &ldquo;Nyonya Delights Pay 1 Dine 2 High Tea.&rdquo;
The updated dessert selection showcases authentic Peranakan treats. Try the kuih lapis, a multi-colored steamed cake made from layers of soft rice flour pudding. Another popular choice is the ang ku kueh, a red tortoise cake.
